<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9beaddba95fb949d26298d814e64c3832.png"></span><span>The Sugary Star</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to stunned enemies by 10%<br>and, when HP is 70% or above, increases attack<br>skill damage by 35%. Also, using Stunning<br>Display will grant the user a strength amp with a<br>maximum team amp level of two. After this amp<br>is granted, this ability will not grant it again for<br>30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/44f0779779abb7a0e021a3d74fdafb9d2.png"></span><span>Potent Poison Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>poisoned them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>Energized: Strength +25%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases strength by 25% for 15 seconds each<br>time the user is energized.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1638856800,update_time1638765819